title: 31 - Kate Willett
itunes:title: 31 - Kate Willett
description: Kate Willett! You may know her from Netflix’s Comedy Lineup, Comedy Central, This Is Not Happening, her own podcast Reply Guys, and generally being a hilarious person around NYC. We all met in San Francisco, hung out in Melbourne, and regularly chill in the city. We’re talking politics, feminism, sexuality, and moving across the country. Here are five words to describe this episode: Chicken Joe will save you.
